content.description: The Wall can be found to the left of A Flakey Situation. It has an odd start that requires a small dyno to a very generous ledge. From the the more difficult part is working your feet up. Follow obvious ledges after the first and walk your way over the top out. V1 grade given for dyno and height.
content.location: Right of trail from Rocky Hollow Picnic Area or follow trail for Tower Parking and walk toward Rocky Hollow Parking.Start can be found directly left of A Flakey Situation. You may have to jump small stream depending on weather.

pathTokens: Rocky Hollow Area at Garret Mountain
